## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of cultural competence challenges in healthcare. Additionally, some sources may not be peer-reviewed, which could affect the reliability of the information. Further research, including empirical studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the challenges and potential solutions.

